{"tid":2309554,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"賓州郵寄選票違憲案件已到達最高法院 , 正等候阿里托大法官批准","createTime":"2020-12-02T15:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T06:06:13.000Z","uid":25468,"like":132,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":56,"replies":[{"pid":"da692f3d0a60ef4fe7719403f90d82d691343f73","tid":2309554,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:27:24.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">Lawsuit by Trump allies challenging Pennsylvania election results reaches Supreme Court</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nA long-shot effort to overturn the presidential election results in Pennsylvania made its way to the Supreme Court Tuesday.<br />\n<br />\nConservative Rep. Mike Kelly, R-Pa., and others contend state officials had no right under the Pennsylvania Constitution to expand mail-in voting in 2019, and the state Supreme Court was wrong to uphold that statute. The group called it &quot;an unconstitutional, no-excuse absentee voting scheme.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Pennsylvania&rsquo;s General Assembly exceeded its powers by unconstitutionally allowing no-excuse absentee voting, including for federal offices, in the election,&quot; the challengers argued in court papers. As a result, the election was &quot;conducted illegally.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe group seeks an emergency injunction from the nation's highest court to block the completion of any remaining steps in the state's certification of Pennsylvania's 2020 election results, which took place last week. The petition was submitted to Associate Justice Samuel Alito.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/2020/12/01/donald-trumps-allies-ask-supreme-court-block-pa-election-result/3785564001/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2F2020%2F12%2F01%2Fdonald-trumps-allies-ask-supreme-court-block-pa-election-result%2F3785564001%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOYLj0gigvT8yTat38OYNh6E%3D&h=c1d8cb96\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/2020/12/01/donald-trumps-allies-ask-supreme-court-block-pa-election-result/3785564001/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/ac/Samuel_Alito_official_photo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fa%2Fac%2FSamuel_Alito_official_photo.jpg&h=f51e7cf3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bc0e713445322b101078fdea657c36d7f917376d","tid":2309554,"uid":310700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fcae1350a5e5b08f50a88808102b5da0df4a3a2","tid":2309554,"uid":158629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4ba06782f8372d532a99ca807d85f1df482fc18","tid":2309554,"uid":383914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec516c5c8897f548359c54022a4e6fccce0f583c","tid":2309554,"uid":18012,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:33:12.000Z","msg":"呢個大法官係保守/自由派?"},{"pid":"198c3e2abbdbac822c9d0bc95a8a3756a3593f30","tid":2309554,"uid":34872,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T15:34:00.000Z","msg":"CC 台左膠又扮叻哥"},{"pid":"8be1b2dd745be2a096cbe96adf841a06ed48e216","tid":2309554,"uid":25468,"like":7,"dislike":0,"scor